<ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">midnight</ENAMEX>, you get most of the benefits, but your <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">spouse</ENAMEX> (who cares about your
health and appearance) shares many of the costs. So a taste for locking the
