<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">ancestors</ENAMEX> (who must have mated successfully or they wouldn't have become
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">ancestors</ENAMEX>) had that taste. The bottom line is that it is intellectually
